== 改编作品 ==

{{main|木乃伊归来|木乃伊3|魔蝎大帝}}
票房上的成功使《木乃伊》之后还拍摄了多部续集和衍生作品。2001年，续集《木乃伊归来》上映，片中包含前作中大部分存活的主要角色，结婚后的里克和伊芙琳对抗印何闐和[[魔蝎大帝|蝎子王]]<ref name="rolling stone- mummy return" />，一同出场的还有里克和伊芙琳的儿子亚历克斯（{{lang|en|Alex}}）<ref name="rolling stone- mummy return">{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/5949327/review/5949328/the_mummy_returns |title=The Mummy Returns |author=Travers, Peter |date=2001-05-09 |work=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2008-04-01 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100106062808/http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/5949327/review/5949328/the_mummy_returns |archivedate = 2010-01-06 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。这部电影也获得了商业上的成功，美国本土票房超过2亿美元，全球票房达到4亿3301万3274美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=mummyreturns.htm |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |title=The Mummy Returns (2001) |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214151710/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=mummyreturns.htm |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-02-14}}</ref>。连续两部电影的成功引领了电视上动画系列剧的诞生并一直播出了两季<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0281471/ |title=The Mummy: The Animated Series (2001– ) |publisher=Amazon |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130717205128/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0281471/ |archivedate=2013-07-17 |work=IMDb |accessdate=2014-02-12 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，还有一部2002年的衍生[[外传|外传]]作品《魔蝎大帝》面世，该片的票房收入也超过1.65亿美元<ref>{{cite web |title=The Scorpion King |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228002706/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=scorpionking.htm |deadurl=no |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=scorpionking.htm |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archivedate=2013-12-28}}</ref>。

2008年8月1日，本片的第二部续集《木乃伊3》上映。故事的背景改为中国，蕾切尔·薇兹的角色改为由[[玛丽亚·贝罗|玛丽亚·贝罗]]（{{lang|en|Maria Bello}}）诠释<ref>{{cite news |author=Garrett, Diane |coauthors=Fleming, Michael |archivedate=2014-02-12 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140212081306/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/fraser-returns-for-mummy-3-2-1117962923/ |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/fraser-returns-for-mummy-3-2-1117962923/ |title=Fraser returns for 'Mummy 3' |publisher=Variety |date=2007-04-11 |accessdate=2014-02-12 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Fleming, Michael |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/bello-replaces-weisz-in-mummy-1117964831/ |title=Bello replaces Weisz in 'Mummy' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140212081406/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/bello-replaces-weisz-in-mummy-1117964831/ |publisher=Variety |date=2007-05-13 |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archivedate=2014-02-12 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。此外，《蝎子王》还通过[[录影带首映|录影带发行]]推出前传《[[蝎子王2：勇士的崛起|蝎子王2：勇士的崛起]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/08/21/173806.php |title=Movie Review — The Scorpion King 2: Rise of a Warrior |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122114607/http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/08/21/173806.php |deadurl=yes |date=2008-08-19 |accessdate=2009-07-27 |work=Blog Critics |last=Peck |first=Aaron |archivedate=2009-01-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |deadurl=no |url=http://www.beyondhollywood.com/the-scorpion-king-2-rise-of-a-warrior-2008-movie-review/ |title=The Scorpion King 2: Rise of a Warrior (2008) Movie Review |date=2008-08-06 |accessdate=2014-02-12 |work=Beyond Hollywood |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120927062453/http://www.beyondhollywood.com/the-scorpion-king-2-rise-of-a-warrior-2008-movie-review/ |author=Nix |archivedate=2012-09-27}}</ref>，不过这两部电影所获评价都很差<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2012-11-02 |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scorpion_king_2/ |title=The Scorpion King 2: Rise of a Warrior (2008) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102155346/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scorpion_king_2/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mummy_tomb_of_the_dragon_emperor/ |title=The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archivedate=2014-01-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104141247/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mummy_tomb_of_the_dragon_emperor/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-mummy-tomb-of-the-dragon-emperor |title=The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archivedate=2012-10-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012032533/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-mummy-tomb-of-the-dragon-emperor |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

